{"tid":2090153,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黎悅澄小姐、黃創暉先生，請你地還錢！","createTime":"2020-07-02T04:28:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T06:46:57.000Z","uid":225264,"like":8,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"134e407576e1fb2601197848e7e18f483d449aef","tid":2090153,"uid":225264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:28:33.000Z","msg":"這個年頭想追人還錢，仲難過問人借錢。<br />\n沒良心的人真的越來越多。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n黃創暉先生與我稱兄道弟，已經是好幾年的好朋友，事源於大約3-4年前，黃先生搞大左他佢當時的女朋友&ndash; 黎悅澄小姐個肚，原本都話要生出來，d fds大家都替佢開心。但後來因為佢私人的事情，就冇生，黃創暉話要帶佢女朋友去私家醫院落bb，當時問我借左4萬。<br />\n當時我都冇<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KAYM9X4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKAYM9X4.png&h=a65c1b9a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z74HJij.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz74HJij.png&h=29a6d75b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CJypWDu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCJypWDu.png&h=e9ee2039&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q2qvSb0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ2qvSb0.png&h=f9015c76&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TzO1YSc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTzO1YSc.png&h=6d8629d6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gyK8DSd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgyK8DSd.png&h=a72522cc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sRBrqxg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsRBrqxg.png&h=25334cf6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iPyhxci.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiPyhxci.png&h=1f02f45b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oV8meqF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoV8meqF.png&h=ed8427b8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2pgNLH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2pgNLH.png&h=f0d9cbe9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n甘多錢，黃創暉先生就叫我幫手問財仔借，ok，因為系兄弟，係好好既朋友，幫。<br />\n時隔甘多年，口口聲聲話會還，但就幾個月比幾千甘，根本就還吾足。<br />\n後來呢幾個月屋企都發生左d問題，都好需要錢救急，我冇理由見住屋企人辛苦，自己絲毫付出吾到？好，甘我就問黃創暉先生還錢，佢原本3月仲有覆我，話4月還，到了4月、5月、6月，都冇再覆過我，都吾聽電話，玩消失。<br />\nOk，甘我揾bb的媽媽，黎悅澄小姐，但黎小姐表示黃創暉都欠佢好多野未還（吾關我事，都唔係我既責任），所以佢吾還錢。簡直是不知所謂，個bb係你 &ndash; 黎悅澄小姐同黃創暉先生既，關我咩事？點解你落仔要我幫你地咩盆數？憑咩？<br />\n你覺得你做野辛苦，揾錢辛苦，人地就吾辛苦，我就吾辛苦？你覺得你落bb你唔需要負責，吾通我就要負責任？咩道理？<br />\n黎悅澄小姐宜家已經另外結左婚，都生左bb，做人阿媽唔係應該更能體會其他人的辛苦？吾通你會想之後你既小朋友都白白辛苦工作，然後d錢拎去比其他人落bb？如果我有甘多錢，我會做d更有意義既事情，而不是比你拎去落bb<br />\n真心唔會再信d咩兄弟，垃圾！<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n如果有巴打認識黃創暉/黎悅澄，唔該幫手聯絡佢，追數，還錢！ thanks"},{"pid":"21803dfc14d07ac51d2199aedc1e9a52c3980f42","tid":2090153,"uid":92941,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:29:32.000Z","msg":"啲錢憑我本事借嘅<br />\n點解要還<br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"8d459fdac8e60114288e1ca89ba888ae6ea4df1d","tid":2090153,"uid":30464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21803dfc14d07ac51d2199aedc1e9a52c3980f42","tid":2090153,"uid":92941,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:29:32.000Z","msg":"啲錢憑我本事借嘅<br />\n點解要還<br />\n屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:29:53.000Z","msg":"岩牙"},{"pid":"be8826a58fc21ef50c688ad33e493dc11a414f6c","tid":2090153,"uid":3976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:29:57.000Z","msg":"tldr<br />\n<br />\nbtw<br />\n<br />\n偉 係到嘛？"},{"pid":"1a24244095279690f97426e0dec17a00dd202d00","tid":2090153,"uid":209657,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:30:01.000Z","msg":"嚇死人咩個樣"},{"pid":"931d75287c732c3d10604572128fd04425dcdf15","tid":2090153,"uid":2501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:30:02.000Z","msg":"乜連登係收數公司？"},{"pid":"79059b934fefe3414a36b7ba2beb1ffb4507d2a6","tid":2090153,"uid":27416,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:30:37.000Z","msg":"自己本